  <version>SUSE Rancher Prime: Cluster API (Turtles)</version>
  <descriptions treatment="append">
    <desc lang="en-us">
        <p>
          SUSE Rancher Prime: Cluster API is a Kubernetes Operator that
          provides integration between SUSE Rancher Prime and Cluster API (CAPI)
          with the aim of bringing full CAPI support to SUSE Rancher Prime. With SUSE
          Rancher Prime: Cluster API, you can automatically import CAPI
          clusters into Rancher and configure the CAPI Operator.
        </p>
      </desc>
  </descriptions>
